3671.description: Order from Chief Mercenary Sophya. Says to destroy the undead at the Execution Grounds.

3672.name: Sophya's 2nd Order
3672.description: Order from Chief Mercenary Sophya. It says to destroy Ol Mahums in the Fortress of Resistance.

3673.name: Sophya's 3rd Order
3673.description: Order from Chief Mercenary Sophya. Says to destroy Delu lizardmen of the southern areas of the Dion and Giran regions.

3674.name: Sophya's 4th Order
3674.description: Order from Chief Mercenary Sophya. Says to destroy marsh stakatos of the Cruma Marshland.

3675.name: Lion's Claw
3675.description: Mark given to the person that achieves distinguished merits in the Black Lion Mercenaries.

3676.name: Lion's Eye
3676.description: Mark given to the person that achieves very distinguished merits in the Black Lion Mercenaries.

3677.name: Guild Coin
3677.description: Commemorative coin given as thanks by the members of the Aden Commercial Guild.

3678.name: Alchemy Text
3678.description: A book that can be obtained from Alchemist Matild. According to the instructions written in the book, go find the secret keeper tree located in the Cruma Marshlands and obtain the secret book.

3679.name: Secret Book of Potion
3679.description: Ancient book received from the guardian trees of the secret. Take this to Alchemist Matild.

3680.name: 1st Potion Recipe
3680.description: Scale of amber basilisk, wind soulstone of whispering wind, glass eye of glass jaguar, blood of Turak bugbear

3681.name: 2nd Potion Recipe

3682.name: Matild's Orb
3682.description: Certificate of Friendship from Alchemist Matild.

3683.name: Forbidden Love Scroll
3683.description: The secrets of depraved but rapturous love are written. May be sold at a high price to an interested person...

3692.name: 1st Circle Hunter License
3692.description: Certificate that proves eligibility as a 1st circle hunter. You must have this to be able to carry out orders given by the Hunter Guild.

3693.name: 2nd Circle Hunter License
3693.description: Certificate that proves eligibility as a 2nd circle hunter. You must have this to be able to carry out orders given by the Hunter Guild.

3694.name: Laurel Leaf Pin
3694.description: Mark given to hunters that successfully carry out requests of the guild. The more experienced a hunter is, the more of these he or she has.

3695.name: 1st Test Instructions
3695.description: Instructions of the test for the 1st circle hunter certificate. Says to complete at least three of the six tasks presented by Grey.

3696.name: 2nd Test Instructions
3696.description: Instructions of the test for the 2nd circle hunter certificate. Says to complete at least three of the six tasks presented by Grey.

3697.name: Cybellin's Request
3697.description: Asks you to raise the purity of blood crystal by killing Leto lizardmen or Harit lizardmen with cybellin dagger.

3698.name: Blood Crystal: Purity 1
3698.description: Bloody jewel that contains dreary magical power. Purity 1. The higher the purity of the crystal is, the higher the value.

3699.name: Blood Crystal: Purity 2
3699.description: Bloody jewel that contains dreary magical power. Purity 2. The higher the purity of the crystal is, the higher the value.
